  "name": "RPlog_Spa_Treatment",
  "title": "A Mandalorian at the Spa",
  "summary": "Aboard the Angry Rancor's luxurious spa, the Nagai Ash coaxes the reluctant Mandalorian soldier Cantrell into a day of relaxation, joining the regular patron Ka'una, a crimson Twi'lek, in the jacuzzi. The group soaks, drinks, and trades banter about hunting expeditions and Cantrell's many battle scars before moving on to massages, where Cantrell's old injuries are worked loose to his groaning delight. They are joined by Nun'ia, the cream-colored Twi'lek cruise manager, who flirts with Cantrell and discusses her planned gladiatorial entertainment events and her dream of opening her own restaurant. The friends talk of self-defense lessons, Nun'ia's promise to Ka'una not to carry a blaster, and the pleasures of the Pleasure Palace before retiring to the lounge, where Nun'ia serves a lavish meal she cooked herself. Over steak, ale, and dessert, the group encourages Nun'ia's restaurant ambitions and lingers in easy companionship until Ash departs for a walk and a hunt, leaving Nun'ia alone with the intimidating but harmless Cantrell.",
